      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation directly correspond to the QoIs used in the regulatory submission claim.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the predicate device regulatory submission and in the ASTM F1717 standard. The validation QoIs are identical to the COU QoIs, providing direct relevance without extrapolation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
