      "rationale": "Validation activities performed using production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs under ASTM F1717 standard conditions, which are identical to the COU geometry and loading. Two independent laboratories participated, providing inter-laboratory reproducibility data. No deviations from COU conditions were introduced. The validation activities are assessed as fully relevant to the COU."
    }
